<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.6.7">
<l>cintaṉaiyait tavaneṟiyait tirumālai piriyātu</l>
<l>vanteṉatu maṉattirunta vaṭamalaiyai varivaṇṭār</l>
<l>kontaṇainta poḻilkōva lulakaḷappā ṉaṭinimirtta</l>
<l>vantaṇaṉai yāṉkaṇṭa taṇinīrtteṉ ṉaraṅkattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My beholding of [the one in my] thoughts, the path of penance, Tirumāl,</l>
<l>The northern mountain which, arising in my mind, is inseparable [from me],</l>
<l>The brahmin of Kōval[ūr], with groves adorned with [flower] clusters</l>
<l rend="indent">full of striped bees,</l>
<l>Who stretched his feet to measure the world,</l>
<l rend="indent">was in Araṅkam of the South by lovely waters.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
